repos.name: BalanceUp
repos.description: BalanceUp is a backend development project for a budget management application.   The app allows users to manage their monthly budgets smartly, as well as data visualization for better financial insights. The backend is developed in Python using the FastAPI framework, with MongoDB as the database.

repos.name: core_MyTaskLog
repos.description: The Task Managment system is a web application designed to facilitate task management within the context of users and administrators. It provides a user-friendly interface to create, update, and delete their tasks, and edit their profile. while administrators have additional privileges to manage users and their own tasks as well.

repos.name: Python-coffee_machine
repos.description: This is a simple Python project simulating a coffee machine. The program allows users to select different types of coffee, manage ingredients, and handle payments. It's designed to demonstrate basic concepts of Python programming, including control structures, functions, and object-oriented programming.

repos.name: Search_jobs_system
repos.description: A full-stack web application that enables users to easily and conveniently search, view, and apply for a wide variety of job opportunities. I built this using Angular for the client side, with ASP.NET Core and C# for the server side, and SQL for the database

repos.name: Second-Hand-Store-Python
repos.description: Python-based terminal application designed to manage a  store that sells both new and second-hand items. The application provides a simple interface for users to view a product catalog, add second-hand items, purchase products, and exit the system.
